column5: You been up to your place lately on Minnitaki? We are heading up in 2 weeks and wondering if the lake is still low. Especially concerned about Abrams chute because we are staying on Abrams Lake. Is the fishing still as great as it always is? Any spots you recommend in the main part of the lake, we normally only go as far as that reef that is to the left after you go thru Harvey's narrows.
